# Network Traffic Prediction

## Overview

This laboratory compared ARIMA, Linear Regression, and Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) models for predicting future network traffic using simulated telecommunications data.

## Technologies

- Python
- Pandas
- Scikit-learn
- PyTorch
- ARIMA
- LSTM

## Skills Developed

- Time-series forecasting
- Feature engineering
- Machine learning
- Deep learning

## Learning Outcome

The project demonstrated how AI models can improve traffic forecasting for next-generation communication networks.
